ngqing Hanchuan Traditional Chinese Medicine for several years. <br><br>Amber specializes in: <br>Pain management, Gastroenterology(digestive disease), <br>Weight control, <br>Gynecology, infertility, <br>Japanese Cosmetic acupuncture<br>the treatment of pre-existing diseases (holistic treatment);\n<br><br>Amber has studied under the famous Japanese acupuncture \u4e2d\u6751\u88d5\u4e5f (the instructor of the Department of Health and Moxibustion Science, Kokoroiryofukushi Training School), the most popular facial techniques in Japan, acupuncture cosmetic and Guasha therapy. <br><br>If you need help with the following conditions, please feel free to consult and see Dr. Amber: <br>\n<br>Urgent and chronic pain;\n<br>Weight control;\n<br>Gastroenterology, including inflammatory bowel diseases such as Crohn&#8217;s disease, ulcerative colitis, irritable bowel syndrome (IBS), habitual constipation or diarrhea; gastritis, stomach pain; Gastric ulcers; Gastroesophageal reflux disease, hemorrhoids, etc. Simple obesity;\n<br>Gynecology, infertility. Including menstrual problems, such as menstrual irregularities, dysmenorrhea, premenstrual syndrome, perimenopausal syndrome, postpartum recovery and conditioning, infertility, recurrent miscarriage, IVF &amp; IUI support treatment.<br>\nJapanese cosmetic acupuncture &amp; Guasha therapy;&nbsp;<br><span data-prop=\"description\" class=\"ck-editable-element\" data-editable=\"basic\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/span><\/p> <div class=\"kv-ee-buttons\">  <\/div><\/div><\/div>  <\/div><div class=\"kv-ee-col-sm-6 align-self-center\"><div data-aspect-ratio=\"\"class=\"kv-ee-original\"> <div data-type=\"image\" data-property=\"image\" style=\"display: flex; height: 100%; align-items: center;\">\n      <img\n         class=\"kv-ee-bg-cover kv-ee-bg-image kv-ee-content-image \"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; padding-bottom: 0;background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;\"\n        data-setting=\"border\"\n   